      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s still in pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it feels brand new! It drives like a dream and has been kept spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that's been truly loved and meticulously maintained, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
