    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive dynamics. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in flawless operational sync. The mechanical provenance is documented, including proactive rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-differential. The chassis retains its factory-correct rigidity with zero bushing deflection, riding on staggered forged alloys. The exterior finish exhibits high-gloss depth with no clear coat failure, while the interior remains a time capsule of Nappa leather and functional analog instrumentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
